This is a "plugin" for the Video Disk Recorder (VDR).

Written by:                  lukkino <dpluca@libero.it>

Project's homepage:          http://kikko77.altervista.org

Latest version available at: http://kikko77.altervista.org

See the file COPYING for license information.


Description:
This plugin load EPG data sent to Mediahighway receivers ( Canal+ group )
or executes external scripts and load EPG data from file.

Command:
Press Up or Down arrow for switch on a provider
Press Ok for start a new scan
Press Back for stop a current scan.


******************************* WARNING *******************************

This plugin work only with vdr >= 1.3.18

***********************************************************************

ATTENTION:
copy a "loadepg.conf" file and "loadepg.equiv" file into a your plugin dir 
for samples my is:

    /video/plugins/loadepg.conf
    /video/plugins/loadepg.equiv


